The '''Rampa Rancors''' were a [[Shockball/Legends|shockball]] team. They once played the [[Dargul Dianogas]] at the [[Innerdome Arena]] of [[Nwarcol Point]]. The [[Abyssin/Legends|Abyssin]] [[Hron]] was the star shock-back of the team.

